  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT315-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">varaiviṭai “āṟṟakiṟṟiyō (G2: vēṟupaṭukiṉṟāy)” eṉṟa tōḻikkuk kiḻatti
          uraittatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Told by HER to the confidante who said “don't you have
          the strength [to await] the time of marriage?” </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT315">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> eḻutaru matiyaṅ kaṭaṟkaṇ ṭāaṅ</l>
          <l> koḻukuveḷ ḷaruvi yōṅkumalai nāṭaṉ</l>
          <l> ñāyi ṟaṉaiyaṉeṉ ṟōḻi</l>
          <l> neruñci yaṉaiyaveṉ perumpaṇait tōḷē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l>The man from the land of high mountains with flowing white waterfalls,</l>
          <l rend="indent2">as if seeing the moon ascend from the sea,</l>
          <l>he [is] like the sun, my friend,</l>
          <l>like Neruñci my big bamboo shoulders.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
